Torrent Search Revolution is a torrent search engine app used to find and download torrent magnet links using multiple sources.

KEY FEATURES
• Search torrents through multiple sources
• Select you favorite sources to perform searches
• Get magnet link and torrent info (title, size, seeds, leeches and category)
• Copy, share or download magnet link (a torrent client app is required to perform downloads on your device)
• Sort results using the torrent sources available criteria
• Favorites list available
• Option to hide results with no seeds in settings page
• Search suggestions available
• Search history list available in settings
• Built-in voice search
• Multiple theme colors and dark mode available
• Pro key for ads removal available (accessible from settings page).
descriptionShort: Search and download torrent magnet links from multiple sources.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Added new search sources
• Bug fixing
• Added loading progress indicator during search process
• The times when advertisements will appear are now clearer
